✨Celebrate your Birthdays Virtually ✨⁣
⁣
Times are hard, we definitely understand. We as Event Planners, know how ᴛᴏᴜɢʜ it is to celebrate your special one’s birthday when all plans have to ᴄᴀɴᴄᴇʟ. ⁣
⁣
But fret not, we are here to 𝓱𝓮𝓵𝓹 you! Who says you can’t have a memorable celebration at 𝓱𝓸𝓶𝓮? ⁣
⁣
We have our 𝓓𝓮𝓪𝓻 Darlene, to share on 6 𝗙𝗨𝗡 ways to celebrate YOUR birthdays ᴠɪʀᴛᴜᴀʟʟʏ during this COVID-19 season🧐  Swipe right to view them ➡️⁣
⁣
We also have an announcement to make....⁣
⁣
Yes! We have just launched our very 𝓷𝓮𝔀 Blog - TheMeetUpSG Blog🙌🏼 Our team have been working really hard on this one😁 ⁣
⁣
❓What is it❓⁣
TheMeetUpSG Blog brings forth various content such as Tips & Tricks, Reviews, How-To's & Exclusive Interviews from Entrepreneurs just for you guys 🤓 From Business Tips📄 to Creamy Pasta Recipes 🍝- we have it all😉 ᴀʟꜱᴏ... we have freebies & giveaways planned as well 🤩  Can't wait to share them with yall 🥳⁣
⁣
What are you waiting for? Click the link on our bio to read more 😉⁣
